-- Auburn Quarterback Cam Newton Allowed to Play After NCAA Investigation
-- B y   E r i k   M a t u s z e w s k i
-- 2010-12-01T18:02:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/auburn-quarterback-cam-newton-allowed-to-play-after-ncaa-investigation.html
Auburn University quarterback Cam
Newton was declared eligible to play by the National Collegiate
Athletic Association after it investigated his recruiting.
The school said a violation occurred and declared him ineligible
two days ago.  The NCAA made the announcement on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Erik Matuszewski in New York at 
 matuszewski@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
